FAIRWOOD GREENS HOMEOWNER'S ASSOCIATION

VOLUME 83 OF PLATS, PAGES 11 THROUGH 14, INCLUSIVE,
RECORDS OF KING COUNTY AUDITOR
2473350110
Grantee claims a lien for unpaid assessments, fines, late fees, interest charges and attorneys' fees and
costs in the amount of $669.16 through October 18, 2021, against the above-described real property.
together with such additional assessments, altorneys' fees, late charges, interest, violation fines, costs,
penalties and other charges as shall accrue against the Property from the date hereof. At time of payment
of the total amount then owing under the provisions and terms of this Lien, Owner or the party remitting
payment will also be required to pay in advance the fees and costs for the preparation and filing of a formal
Release of Lien.
Unofficial Copy
Dated this _18_day of October, 2021.
ERIK R. OLSEN, being sworn, says: I am the attorney for the claimant above-named: I have read the
foregoing Notice of Claim of Lien, know the contents thereof, and believe the same to be true.
